                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1va">ff. 1va-2</locus>
                           <desc>vb: Supplications from the Daily Office (cp. MQ p. 295), chants
                              from the Ordinary of the Mass (MQ, 1955 E.C., cp. pp. 49-50), partly
                              unidentified. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#1va">1va</locus>: እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚእ፡ ኢዘሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አምላክነ፡
                              ዘትቤሎ፡ ለፍቁርከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ …</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> Chants from the Ordinary of the Mass (<locus from="2rb" to="2vb">2rb-2vb</locus>
                           <note>) has been written in script of smaller size. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#2vb">f. 2vb</locus>
                           <desc>: Heading of Text I mentioning the name of the donor in the
                              supplication formula. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#2vb">2vb</locus>: ኪዳን፡ ዘነግህ፡ ዝነገሮሙ፡ በአባዊነ፡ ሐዋርያት፡
                              እምቅድመ፡ ዕርገቱ፡…</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The heading written entirely in red ink has been added later.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc> </desc>
                           <desc>f.122vb: Donation note. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">f.122vb: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘወይዘሮ፡ ትብለጽ፡ ስመ፡ አቡሃ፡ ገብረ፡
                              ሕይወት…</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> wayzaro<note> Tǝbläṣ is mentioned as the donor,
                              other family members are also mentioned. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Omitted passages have been written in small script in
                           the upper margin: <locus target="#8r">8r</locus>, 31r, 34v, 35r, 72v,
                           73r, 80v, 83v, 85v, 109v. 
 - Crude notes: <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>.</item>
                     </list>
